lead_paragraph: Ten-man AC Milan missed the chance to take provisional top spot in Serie A as they slumped to a 3-0 defeat at Genoa with Gabriel Paletta sent off and Juraj Kucka scoring an own goal on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Ten-Man Milan Miss Out on Top Spot in 3-0 Defeat at Genoa
